This project is made by three students of the university of applied sciences Windesheim located in Zwolle the Netherlands.
This project contains two software programs. One is console program which you'll need to run on a laptop or computer which is able
to connect to devices via bluetooth. The other program is the one for the microcontroller for the robot.  
Please download the schematic files for all the hardware information. 
For detailled information please Read the Elektor Article (Dutch only)

Please visit https://youtu.be/tjqIGv0BcZE for a demonstration of the final product
